<text id="02-output-contract" title="Spring Boot Patterns Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema for the layered-service manifest this methodology produces. Validator enforces required keys + per-field constraints.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/java-spring-boot.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["spring_boot_version", "stack", "uses_records_for_dtos", "uses_mapstruct", "uses_problemdetail_advice", "injection_style"],
  "properties": {
    "spring_boot_version": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^3\\."},
    "stack": {"const": "webmvc"},
    "uses_records_for_dtos": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "uses_mapstruct": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "uses_problemdetail_advice": {"type": "boolean", "const": true},
    "injection_style": {"const": "constructor"},
    "transactional_layer": {"const": "service"},
    "forbidden_patterns_found": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "string"}, "maxItems": 0}
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "spring_boot_version": "3.2.1",
  "stack": "webmvc",
  "uses_records_for_dtos": true,
  "uses_mapstruct": true,
  "uses_problemdetail_advice": true,
  "injection_style": "constructor",
  "transactional_layer": "service",
  "forbidden_patterns_found": []
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "spring_boot_version": "2.7.0",
  "stack": "webflux",
  "uses_records_for_dtos": false,
  "uses_mapstruct": false,
  "uses_problemdetail_advice": false,
  "injection_style": "field",
  "transactional_layer": "controller",
  "forbidden_patterns_found": ["@Autowired field injection in UserService"]
}
]]></code>
    <note>Boot 2.x; reactive stack; class DTOs sharing entity; no MapStruct; no ProblemDetail; field injection; @Transactional on controller.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>`@Autowired` on a field.</item>
      <item>Controller returning a JPA entity.</item>
      <item>`BeanUtils.copyProperties(entity, dto)` mapping.</item>
      <item>`try/catch` in controllers for cross-cutting concerns (use `@RestControllerAdvice`).</item>
      <item>`@Transactional` on a controller method.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-java-spring-boot.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
